<div class="modal" id="delete-modal">
  <div class="modal-content modal-sm">
    <button class="modal-close" type="button" data-modal-close="delete-modal">×</button>
    <div class="modal-header">
      <h4>O'chirishni tasdiqlang</h4>
      <p>Bu amal qaytarilmaydi. Davom etishdan oldin yozuv to'g'riligini tekshiring.</p>
    </div>
    <form id="delete-form" method="POST">
      <div class="modal-actions">
        <button class="btn-secondary" type="button" data-modal-close="delete-modal">Yo'q</button>
        <button class="btn-danger" type="submit">Ha, o'chirish</button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>
